# Walkthrough - Responsive Reviews Grid

Implemented responsive design updates for the `[ocean_reviews_grid_test]` shortcode to improve readability on smaller screens.

## Changes

Modified [inc/reviews-test.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/ocean/wp-content/themes/hello-elementor-child/inc/reviews-test.php) to include specific media queries.

### Responsive Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Device Target | Font Size (Text) | Font Size (Author) | Card Padding | Navigation |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **> 1500px** | Default / Large | 20px | 20px | 40px | Side Arrows |
| **1251px - 1500px** | Laptop | 18px | 20px | 35px | Side Arrows (adjusted) |
| **768px - 1250px** | Tablet | 17px | 18px | 30px | Side Arrows (adjusted) |
| **< 767px** | Mobile | 15px | 16px | 20px | **Bottom Arrows (Centered)** |

### Code Updates

Refactored the `<style>` block to organize breakpoints and override base styles appropriately.

```css
        /* Mobile (< 767px) */
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
             /* Stack columns, make space for arrows at bottom */
            .ocean-reviews-slide { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .ocean-reviews-slider-wrapper { padding-bottom: 60px; }
            
            /* Position arrows at bottom center */
            .ocean-reviews-arrow {
                display: flex;
                top: auto; bottom: 0;
                transform: none;
            }
            .ocean-reviews-arrow.prev { left: calc(50% - 60px); }
            .ocean-reviews-arrow.next { right: calc(50% - 60px); }
        }
```

